81
00:07:14,633 --> 00:07:16,655
And we managed to stay.

82
00:07:16,755 --> 00:07:23,121
They actually offered the place as a training site for police, and they would blow down doors, they had flashbangs.

83
00:07:23,661 --> 00:07:32,188
I mean, it felt like a war with guns going off, and we put a big sign on the door saying, we're here, don't blow our door down.

84
00:07:33,387 --> 00:07:34,348
You were in the middle of it.

85
00:07:34,409 --> 00:07:34,609
Yeah.

86
00:07:34,789 --> 00:07:36,532
