00:19:18,513 --> 00:19:19,933
It's really interesting.

274
00:19:19,953 --> 00:19:21,334
It's actually work in a darkroom.

275
00:19:21,735 --> 00:19:27,762
and we gain friends of the darkroom and friends of the community and we've actually had a marriage come about because of that.

276
00:19:27,782 --> 00:19:28,903
Well there you go!

277
00:19:29,103 --> 00:19:29,744
Wow!

278
00:19:30,965 --> 00:19:38,794
But no, it's really, it's, I remember I started when I was nine years old and it was my dad's hobby and once a week we turned the bathroom into a darkroom.

279
00:19:39,395 --> 00:19:39,855
Okay.

280
00:19:39,996 --> 00:19:41,517
The Jean Dark he called it.

281
00:19:41,537 --> 00:19:42,218
That had to be a...

282
